{"tid":1235653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢刻要搶民意, 就要狙擊中信","createTime":"2019-06-17T08:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T10:18:42.000Z","uid":54785,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6e100a25b593f68d8e8f00a9acf40ac4b41187ad","tid":1235653,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"612 當日係中信和平示威區, 大台警告警方後退, 因人群已退後至和平示威區範圍, 亦已證實大台有不反對通知書, 而警方仍以不當武力清場, 發射至少8顆催淚彈, 場面混亂, 毫無反抗能力的示威人士與大批傷者在恐慌下意圖衝入中信避難, 有多人哮喘發作, 險發生人踩人慘劇。<br />\n<br />\n呢刻警方想搶民意, 改善形象, 但中信件事而家先逐步浮面, 佢地一定要交代, 唔可以輕易比佢地洗白<br />\n<br />\n中信苦主們會整合一個集中討論post, 請大家呢刻集中火力要求警方交代事件, 以及要求議員聲討"},{"pid":"e4c83954df4ea3aa0f8dd7fcaffa39635724f53d","tid":1235653,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:04:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d13757b0e4664568d242ce1d0b704a0934462e4","tid":1235653,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/juERb4D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjuERb4D.png&h=52180b62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf8cc916c868fd237161775d768e780c47b925a5","tid":1235653,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:05:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5ce36d7f8f73d57c578785762a4193e39d5efc7","tid":1235653,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caf29ecd7503eb1662e50c226c58667ede14e04f","tid":1235653,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87de482c8d55c308d349407e83f74abaeac1402","tid":1235653,"uid":119667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:16:04.000Z","msg":"當時我夢到嘅情況<br />\n黑線係黑警路線<br />\n紅色係路障<br />\n綠色係示威者逃生路線<br />\n紫色係催淚彈攻擊位置(大概)<br />\n但確認第一彈係係路障裡面<br />\n因為我就係隔離<br />\n<img src=\"https://